comment: Alternate proof of ~ bj-nuliota . Note that this alternate proof uses the fact that ` iota x ph ` evaluates to ` (/) ` when there is no ` x ` satisfying ` ph ` ( ~ iotanul ). This is an implementation detail of the encoding currently used in set.mm and should be avoided. (Contributed by BJ, 30-Nov-2019.) (Proof modification is discouraged.) (New usage is discouraged.)
